casebody.data:
No. 80,

Orig.

Colorado v. New Mexico et al. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 449 U. S. 1007.]

Report of the Special Master on the Equitable Apportionment of the Vermejo River is received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs to the Report may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Reply briefs, if any, to such Exceptions may be filed within 30 days.
